<plot>This is a documentary about two Jewish lesbians getting a Jewish marriage. They interview the rabbi, the family members, especially one of the mothers who has a hard time coping with the fact that their daughter is a lesbian. They go through their feeling for each other, and what kind of wedding they want, and how to do it...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?102715</url></doc>
